        "subject": "LU-13643 mdt: Eviction detection for AW locks",
        "message": "LU-13643 mdt: Eviction detection for AW locks\n\nWe need to know when an active writer lock cancellation\nis due to eviction.  Add code to detect this.\n\nEventually, we will give this special handling, where it\nmarks certain mirrors inconsistent.  Tentatively, we'll\nhave it mark all mirrors except the primary one\ninconsistent.\n\nThere's an issue here, though - what if there are other\nerrors from other AW locks?  It's not quite clear how\nto handle that, so this is more by way of a note of\nwhat's possible than a serious patch.\n\nNote: It also removes the active writer lock cancellation\nand ageing policies to make testing this easier.\n(Ageing policy patch is just excluded from this history)\n\nThis is confirmed to work by looking at debug logs.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I9423bbcd38731dbee6dd1d319b53ef7d3428182f\n"
      },
